OL,4,Cplayer in rampage outside nightclub
OL,6,FA man who went on a 'knife rampage'
OL,7,Foutside a Bodmin nightclub has been
OL,8,Ffound guilty of murder.
OL,10,FJake Hill, 25, stabbed several people
OL,11,Foutside the Eclipse nightclub with a
OL,12,Ftactical combat knife, killing 32-year-
OL,13,Fold rugby player Michael Riddiough-
OL,14,FAllen.
OL,16,FOn Thursday 14 March, a jury found
OL,17,FHill guilty of murdering Michael
OL,18,FRiddiough-Allen who Truro Crown Court
OL,19,Fheard had tried to break up a fight in
OL,20,Fthe early hours of 30 April 2023.
