OL,6,FThe jury heard how Hill's victims were
OL,7,Feither stabbed or slashed after he
OL,8,Fcollected the blade from a nearby
OL,9,Fhedge, where he had hidden it prior to
OL,10,Fentering the nightclub.
OL,12,FHill has also been convicted of four
OL,13,Fcounts of wounding with intent. He was
OL,14,Fcleared of a fifth count of wounding
OL,15,Fwith intent.
OL,17,FChelsea Powell, aged 22 of Granny's
OL,18,FGreen, was found not guilty of murder
OL,19,Fand manslaughter. She was found guilty
OL,20,Fof perverting the course of justice.
