OL,6,FTia Taylor, also 22, of Northey Road,
OL,7,Fadmitted charges during the trial of
OL,8,Fmanslaughter and perverting the course
OL,9,Fof justice.
OL,11,FPowell and Taylor both deliberately
OL,12,Flied to frustrate the police in their
OL,13,Finvestigation.
OL,15,FHill was found hiding in the loft at
OL,16,FTaylor's address following the
OL,17,Fstabbing after she told officers
OL,18,Fnobody else was home.
