OL,4,Cplayer in rampage outside nightclub
OL,6,F"There are no winners here. It is not
OL,7,Fjust our family who lost someone they
OL,8,Floved that night.
OL,10,F"The families of Tia Taylor, Chelsea
OL,11,FPowell and Jake Hill, have been torn
OL,12,Fapart by the evil of that night - the
OL,13,Fpresence of a knife.
OL,15,F"With no knife the devastating events
OL,16,Fof that night would not have happened.
OL,17,FThe presence and use of a knife turned
OL,18,Fto unmitigated violence, scarring
OL,19,Finjuries and haunting images that many
OL,20,Fwill never forget.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
