OL,6,FDetective Constable Emma Norrish, of
OL,7,FDevon & Cornwall Police's Major Crime
OL,8,FInvestigation Team, said: "We welcome
OL,9,Fthe verdict reached by the jury after
OL,10,Fhearing the evidence and deliberating
OL,11,Fon their decisions.
OL,13,F"This has been a long and complex
OL,14,Finvestigation and trial and we now
OL,15,Fawait the sentencing of the three
OL,16,Fdefendants.
OL,18,F"I hope the outcome reached today will
OL,19,Fbegin to bring some closure to
OL,20,FMichael's family and friends, and to
OL,21,Fthe surviving victims."
